[One paragraph: what would flip the verdict. Example: "The Medium VfM rating is robust to a ±20% shift in benefits or costs. The Effectiveness rating would drop to Low only if additionality falls below 50% (central case assumes 75%). Unit cost benchmarks are based on 2024 data; any significant wage inflation would tighten the Economy rating."]

